title: The Pregnancy Fitness Rules That Matter Most, with Taylor Walker Sinning
description:
Pregnancy fitness expert Taylor Walker Sinning is on to talk about her new pregnancy fitness program on the Fitness App. She covers everything from top pregnancy fitness rules to essential health care strategies pre and post natal! Plus, she has life changing advice on how to heal diastasis recti, recover from a c-section, and manage postpartum.
